{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9c475a441b","title":"致第一二师负责人等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d9efd08642","index":0,"year":1938,"month":6,"day":15,"articleId":"9c475a441b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4d351a18b9","type":"paragraph","text":"致第一二师负责人等电\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"9c475a441b"},{"id":"a6764f82d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年6月15日）目前是否可以向傅作义及其他军政首长提议，召集晋西北及绥东各部队首长（连游击队在内）、各政府与民众团体的领袖开一个会议，讨论如何打退日军进攻、保卫音西北的作战计划，并相机提出建立根据地的某些重要问题。电报指出，只要情况允许，这个会议召集成功，是可能解决许多问题、推进统一战线的。1]这是毛泽东关于日军又向晋西北进攻问题和胡腰（刘少奇）致第一二O师负责人并告朱德、彭德怀电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"9c475a441b"}],"page":{"id":"fe143f359b","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"9c475a441b","start":357,"end":357}}}},"__N_SSG":true}